# Implement Invite Employee Feature (Section 4.2)

## Codebase Findings Summary

### Backend
- **Invite CRUD is already fully implemented** in [AuthController.cs](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/api/InnerG.Api/Controllers/AuthController.cs) + [AuthService.cs](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/api/InnerG.Api/Services/Interfaces/IAuthService.cs) at `/api/auth/invites`
  - `POST /api/auth/invites` ‚Üí create single invite
  - `POST /api/auth/invites/bulk` ‚Üí bulk invite
  - `POST /api/auth/invites/{id}/resend` ‚Üí resend
  - `POST /api/auth/invites/{id}/revoke` ‚Üí revoke
  - Token = Base64Url-encoded random bytes (not SHA256)
  - Role stored in `RolesCsv` on [Invite](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/api/InnerG.Api/Models/Invite.cs#5-25) model (confirmed)
- **Missing from backend:**
  - `GET /api/auth/invites` ‚Äî paginated list with filters (status, search)
  - `POST /api/auth/invites/validate-file` ‚Äî CSV/Excel parse & validate

### Frontend
- **Tailwind v4** ‚Äî tokens in [index.css](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/web/src/index.css): `--color-primary: #13ecb6`, `--color-deep-blue: #0a192f`, `--color-bg-light: #f6f8f8`, font `Manrope`
- **API**: `import api from './api/axios'` (default export)
- **Toast**: `react-hot-toast`, `import toast from 'react-hot-toast'`
- **Queries**: React Query v5, `useQuery` / `useMutation`
- **Pattern** matches [MembersPage.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/web/src/pages/hr/MembersPage/MembersPage.tsx) ‚Äî no base class, inline Tailwind classes
- **Routes** in [AppRoutes.jsx](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/web/src/routes/AppRoutes.jsx) ‚Üí add `/invitations` under `AppLayout` protected by `['hr']`
- **No existing invitations pages or components**

