### Frontend

#### [NEW] [invitation.types.ts](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/web/src/types/invitation.types.ts)
Type definitions matching backend DTOs.

#### [NEW] [invitationsApi.ts](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/web/src/api/invitationsApi.ts)
API calls:
- [getList(params)](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/web/src/api/memberApi.ts#4-8) ‚Üí `GET /auth/invites`
- `createSingle(data)` ‚Üí `POST /auth/invites`
- `validateFile(file)` ‚Üí `POST /auth/invites/validate-file`
- `bulkSend(invites)` ‚Üí `POST /auth/invites/bulk`
- `resend(id)` ‚Üí `POST /auth/invites/{id}/resend`
- [revoke(id)](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/web/src/api/memberApi.ts#24-28) ‚Üí `POST /auth/invites/{id}/revoke`

#### [NEW] [useInvitations.ts](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/web/src/hooks/hr/useInvitations.ts)
`useQuery` for invite list with filters.

#### [NEW] [useInvitationActions.ts](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/web/src/hooks/hr/useInvitationActions.ts)
`useMutation` for revoke, resend, single invite. Each invalidates `['invitations']`.

#### [NEW] [useBulkInvite.ts](file:///c:/Users/ACER/Desktop/Ky%208/EXE102/innerg/web/src/hooks/hr/useBulkInvite.ts)
Two separate mutations: `validateFile` and `bulkSend`. State machine: `'upload' | 'preview' | 'result'`.

